---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import GreenBlock from '../components/GreenBlock.astro';
import VerticalCard from '../components/VerticalCard.astro';
---
<Base title="MPower" current="Home" description="MPower - a subscription community that equips people with the knowledge, power and skills to grow, thrive and flourish, without relying on anyone else for the answers. Pre-launch in Aotearoa NZ, 2026.">

  {/* Hero ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */}
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="mono hero-kicker">§ Launching soon · NZ based, globally relevant, future focused · 2026</div>
      <h1 class="display hero-title">
        Knowledge. <span class="i-accent">Power.</span> Yours.
      </h1>
      <p class="body-lg hero-sub">
        MPower is the answer you came for... in your language, on your phone, in the moment you need it. We're built so people don't need us ... but stay because you love being part of our community and keep growing, thriving and flourishing. <span class="accent">Equip2MPower.</span>
      </p>
      <div class="hero-ctas">
        <a href="/waitlist" class="btn btn-primary">Join the waitlist <span class="arr">→</span></a>
        <a href="/about" class="btn btn-ghost">Read why <span class="arr">→</span></a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  {/* Founder story ────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */}
  <section class="section-tight">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="founder">
        <figure class="media founder-photo">
          <div class="media-frame"><img src="/images/lisa.jpg" alt="Lisa Shaw, Founder of MPower." loading="lazy" /></div>
          <figcaption class="mono">§ Lisa · Founder · Aotearoa New Zealand</figcaption>
        </figure>
        <div class="founder-body">
          <span class="mono founder-eyebrow">§ In Lisa's words (our founder's story)</span>
          <h2 class="display founder-h">I learned most of what I know <span class="i-accent">the hard way.</span></h2>
          <p class="body-lg">Figured it out as I went. Made mistakes I never needed to make, because <span class="i-accent">nobody took the time to teach me</span>, and the people who could have held their knowledge tight. I want to change that.</p>
          <p class="body founder-graf">I'm a recovering accountant who runs businesses (I'm not a "theoretical only" leader), made payroll with no cash in the bank, sits on boards, and works with leaders from all walks of life trying to understand how to solve the problems they are facing. I got so annoyed at hearing "no-one trains you for this". We need to do something radically different. They are different rooms, different sectors, but the same thing every time - the expertise existed somewhere, it just never reached the person who needed it, not in their language, not in the moment it mattered. Capable and passionate people, made to feel like they were the only one who didn't know, and didn't know how to find the right answers. We promote people into leadership roles because they are technically capable, BUT, we never teach them how to lead.</p>
          <p class="body founder-graf">That's why I built MPower. Not another course library. A place where you get the knowledge, the power and the skills to <span class="i-accent">grow, thrive and flourish</span>, in plain language, with nobody gatekeeping the info, talking down to you, or making you feel like you're dumb.</p>
          <p class="body-lg">My whole working life has come down to one question: how do we <span class="i-accent">equip</span> people so they're genuinely <span class="i-accent">empowered</span>, then get out of their way? MPower is that question, built.</p>
          <p class="display founder-closer">You were always capable. Now you're <span class="i-accent">equipped.</span></p>
          <p class="mono founder-sign">Lisa Shaw · Founder and Chief Empowerment Officer, MPower · May 2026</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  {/* Manifesto ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */}
  <section class="manifesto">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="mf-kicker mono">§ 01 · The manifesto</div>
      <h2 class="mf-statement display" style="color: var(--c-spring);">
        We believe <span style="color: var(--c-mist);">YOU</span> are already capable.
      </h2>
      <p class="mf-subline display">Actually, we <span class="mf-know">KNOW</span> you are.</p>
      <div class="mf-body">
        <aside class="mf-side">
          <span class="mono">§ The why</span>
          <p class="mf-aside body-sm">The world doesn't lack for expertise. It lacks people genuinely wanting to build each other up, help each other out and equip them so they are empowered. We're on a mission to change that!</p>
        </aside>
        <div class="mf-prose">
          <p class="body-lg mf-lede">You just need the right tools, in the right place, in your language. You don't know what you don't know ... right? Good and accessible knowledge is locked behind paywalls, buried in jargon, sitting in offices (or heads) of people who don't share.</p>
          <p class="body mf-graf">That's a delivery failure, not a capability gap. MPowered is what people become. The italic <span class="i-accent">2</span> in our tagline is the bridge between knowing and doing. Equip you. Then empower you.</p>
          <p class="body mf-graf">We're designing for real people. We're listening to your stories, your challenges, what you are wanting. What works for a person on a farm in a remote Waikato village will work for a CEO in an ivory tower, the converse is seldom true.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <hr class="rule mf-rule" />
      <p class="mf-pull display">
        Success looks like the day you <span class="i-accent">don't need us</span> anymore ... but you stay because you love being part of our community, and keep <span class="i-accent">growing, thriving, flourishing.</span>
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  {/* Green statement ───────────────────────────────────────────────────── */}
  <GreenBlock
    kicker="§ The why behind the work"
    cta={{ href: '/about', label: 'Read the why' }}
  >
    <h2>Built so you <em>don't need us</em> anymore.</h2>
    <p>
      People are already capable. They just need the right tools, in the right place, in their own language. The world doesn't lack for expertise, it lacks for delivery.
    </p>
  </GreenBlock>

  {/* Phase 1 communities ───────────────────────────────────────────────── */}
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-head">
        <span class="mono">§ 02 · Our communities · Phase 1</span>
        <h2 class="display" style="font-size: var(--t-h2); max-width: 18ch;">
          One open now. <span class="i-accent">Two launching next.</span>
        </h2>
      </div>

      <div style="margin-bottom: 24px;">
        <VerticalCard
          name="Teams"
          badge="Available now · MPower Teams"
          tagline="Your team. Your context."
          body="Leadership development built around your team, your context and your growth trajectory - ongoing, not a one-workshop wonder. Open now, by arrangement."
          url="mailto:askme@mpowerhq.nz?subject=MPower Teams enquiry"
          host="askme@mpowerhq.nz"
          accent="var(--c-bronze)"
          ink="var(--c-amber)"
        />
      </div>

      <div class="vert-grid">
        <VerticalCard
          name="Agri"
          badge="01 · MPower Agri"
          tagline="The business side of farming, finally in one place."
          body="For whoever runs the business side of a farming operation - the people, the payroll, the money, the strategy, the succession. The stuff nobody showed you, with no one place to learn it. You can find an agronomist, a vet, a stock agent. There's no equivalent for the business side. This is it - plain language, no judgment, from people who've done it, and nobody ever selling you anything."
          url="https://agri.mpowerhq.nz"
          host="agri.mpowerhq.nz"
          accent="var(--c-clay)"
          ink="var(--c-wheat)"
          tags={[['Clay','#C04B26'],['Wheat','#FFD9A8'],['Earth','#8B2F15'],['Soil','#2D1810']]}
        />
        <VerticalCard
          name="Ed"
          badge="02 · MPower Ed"
          tagline="Leadership for everyone who learns. For everyone who teaches."
          body="Yours is the one trade whose whole job is to pass it on - and the people leading it get the least support for the leadership side. Built for principals, board chairs, department heads, training leads, kura and ECE management. The tools, the language, and a community leading the same load, so you're not carrying it on your own."
          url="https://ed.mpowerhq.nz"
          host="ed.mpowerhq.nz"
          accent="var(--c-indigo)"
          ink="var(--c-gold)"
          tags={[['Indigo','#818CF8'],['Gold','#FCD34D'],['Night','#1E1B4B'],['Page','#E0E7FF']]}
        />
      </div>

      <div class="vert-future">
        <div class="mono">§ 02 · More communities - coming soon</div>
        <div class="vert-grid">
          <VerticalCard
            name="Leaders"
            tagline="Coaching and community."
            body="For individuals who want the benefit of coaching and a community that has their back - a place to grow alongside others on the same path."
            accent="var(--c-violet)"
            ink="var(--c-lilac)"
            coming={true}
          />
          <VerticalCard
            name="Rising"
            tagline="Headstart and habits."
            body="Our next generation of leaders - giving them a headstart in the world, with the language and habits of leadership before they need them."
            accent="var(--c-cyan)"
            ink="var(--c-mint)"
            coming={true}
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  {/* How it works ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */}
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-head">
        <span class="mono">§ How it works</span>
        <h2 class="display" style="font-size: var(--t-h2); max-width: 22ch;">
          Real answers. <span class="i-accent">No jargon. No gatekeepers.</span>
        </h2>
      </div>

      <ol class="steps">
        <li>
          <span class="step-num">01</span>
          <h3 class="heading step-title">Find us free on social.</h3>
          <p class="body step-body">The genuinely useful stuff lives out in the open - no paywall, no sign-up, nobody locked out.</p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <span class="step-num">02</span>
          <h3 class="heading step-title">Come inside when you're ready.</h3>
          <p class="body step-body">Join your community on a 30-day trial: the full resource library in plain language, and people doing exactly what you're doing.</p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <span class="step-num">03</span>
          <h3 class="heading step-title">Grow until you don't need us.</h3>
          <p class="body step-body">Use it, make it yours, pass it on. We measure success by the day you can answer for yourself.</p>
        </li>
      </ol>

      <a href="/how-it-works" class="btn btn-ghost" style="margin-top: 56px;">
        Read the full principle <span class="arr">→</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

</Base>

<style>
  /* Hero -------------------------------------------------------------- */
  .hero { padding-block: clamp(80px, 12vw, 180px) clamp(48px, 6vw, 80px); }
  .hero-kicker { color: var(--c-spring); margin-bottom: 32px; }
  .hero-title {
    font-size: var(--t-display);
    max-width: 14ch;
    line-height: 0.92;
  }
  .hero-sub {
    margin-top: clamp(28px, 3vw, 44px);
    max-width: 60ch;
    font-size: var(--t-body-lg);
    opacity: .9;
  }
  .hero-ctas {
    display: flex; gap: 14px; flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-top: clamp(36px, 4vw, 56px);
  }

  /* Founder ----------------------------------------------------------- */
  .founder {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 0.9fr 1.1fr;
    gap: clamp(28px, 5vw, 72px);
    align-items: start;
    max-width: 1120px;
    margin-inline: auto;
  }
  .founder-photo { margin: 0; }
  .founder-photo .media-frame img { aspect-ratio: 4 / 5; }
  .founder-body { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 20px; padding-top: 8px; }
  .founder-eyebrow { color: var(--c-fog); }
  .founder-h { font-size: var(--t-h2); line-height: 1.05; max-width: 18ch; margin: 0; }
  .founder-body p { max-width: 56ch; margin: 0; }
  .founder-graf { color: var(--c-mist); opacity: .9; }
  .founder-closer {
    font-size: clamp(28px, 2.4vw, 38px);
    line-height: 1.15; max-width: 22ch;
    margin: 8px 0 0 0; letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }
  .founder-sign { margin-top: 8px; color: var(--c-mist); letter-spacing: 0.08em; }
  @media (max-width: 860px) {
    .founder { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 24px; }
    .founder-photo { max-width: 420px; }
  }

  /* Shared media figure ----------------------------------------------- */
  .media { margin: 0; }
  .media-frame { border-radius: 4px; overflow: hidden; border: 1px solid var(--c-rule-soft); }
  .media-frame img { display: block; width: 100%; height: auto; aspect-ratio: 16 / 9; object-fit: cover; filter: saturate(.92) brightness(.97); }
  .media figcaption { font-family: var(--f-mono); font-size: var(--t-mono); letter-spacing: .1em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--c-fog); padding-top: 12px; }

  /* Manifesto --------------------------------------------------------- */
  .manifesto { padding-block: clamp(80px, 10vw, 140px); border-top: 1px solid var(--c-rule); }
  .mf-kicker { color: var(--c-spring); margin-bottom: 32px; letter-spacing: 0.18em; }
  .mf-statement {
    font-size: clamp(56px, 7vw, 104px);
    line-height: 1.0;
    letter-spacing: -0.035em;
    max-width: 22ch;
    padding-bottom: 0.1em;
  }
  .mf-subline {
    font-size: clamp(28px, 3.6vw, 52px);
    line-height: 1.05;
    letter-spacing: -0.025em;
    margin: 18px 0 0;
    max-width: 22ch;
    font-weight: 500;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--c-mist);
  }
  .mf-know { font-style: normal; font-weight: 800; color: var(--c-spring); letter-spacing: 0.02em; }
  .mf-body {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 2.4fr;
    gap: clamp(40px, 6vw, 96px);
    margin-top: clamp(48px, 6vw, 80px);
  }
  .mf-side .mono { color: var(--c-spring); display: block; margin-bottom: 14px; }
  .mf-aside { font-style: italic; opacity: .85; max-width: 28ch; }
  .mf-prose { max-width: 62ch; }
  .mf-lede { font-size: clamp(20px, 1.8vw, 26px); line-height: 1.5; opacity: .92; }
  .mf-graf { margin-top: 24px; opacity: .85; }
  .mf-rule { margin-top: clamp(56px, 6vw, 88px); }
  .mf-pull {
    font-size: clamp(40px, 5vw, 72px);
    line-height: 1.04;
    letter-spacing: -0.035em;
    max-width: 24ch;
    margin-top: clamp(36px, 4vw, 56px);
    padding-bottom: 0.1em;
  }
  @media (max-width: 860px) {
    .mf-body { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }

  /* Verticals --------------------------------------------------------- */
  .vert-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 24px;
  }
  .vert-future { margin-top: clamp(64px, 7vw, 96px); }
  .vert-future > .mono { color: var(--c-fog); margin-bottom: 24px; display: block; }
  @media (max-width: 860px) {
    .vert-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }

  /* Steps ------------------------------------------------------------- */
  .steps {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 0;
  }
  .steps li {
    padding: 32px 28px 32px 0;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--c-rule);
    display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 14px;
  }
  .step-num {
    font-family: var(--f-display);
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--c-spring);
    font-size: clamp(36px, 4vw, 56px);
    line-height: 1;
    letter-spacing: -0.04em;
  }
  .step-title { font-size: var(--t-h4); }
  .step-body  { max-width: 36ch; opacity: .85; }

  @media (max-width: 860px) {
    .steps { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
</style>
